<section id="about" class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-bg-soft">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-in">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text-primary">Who We Are</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto fade-in">
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-8">
        We're a small team that builds and operates the exact systems we deploy for clients.
        No account managers, no layers of overhead. When you work with us, you work directly
        with the people who design and build your systems.
      </p>
      <div class="bg-white border border-border rounded-2xl p-8 flex items-start gap-6">
        <img
          src="/portrait.jpeg"
          alt="Antoine Miniconi"
          class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full object-cover object-top flex-shrink-0"
        />
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-3">Antoine Miniconi</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Built and operated automated B2B sales systems that generated over $1M in revenue
            before turning the same approach into a service for clients. He's built the pipelines,
            run the outreach, and closed the deals himself. When he builds your system, he knows
            what works because he's done it for his own business first.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-8 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
        We don't just advise — we build, deploy, and stand behind what we deliver.
        That's the difference.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
